legs.end_address: Foz do Iguaçu, State of Paraná, Brazil

steps.html_instructions:
Head south on Av. Miguel Rosa toward Av. Higino Cunha/Av. Joaquim Ribeiro
Pass by the pharmacy (on the right in 2 km)
Keep left to continue on Av. Prefeito Wall Ferraz
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto BR-230/BR-343
Keep left to continue on Av. Dr. José Ribamar Pachêco

At the roundabout, continue straight onto Av. Calixto Lôbo/PI-140
Continue to follow PI-140
Turn left onto R. Joao Climaco de Almeida

Turn right onto BR-135/BR-343
Continue to follow BR-135
BR-135 turns slightly right and becomes Anel Viário de Bertolínia
Slight right to stay on Anel Viário de Bertolínia
